    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tochiman-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tochiman-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chk",
      "speakerName": "高海千歌",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chk.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chk_01_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_chk_01_01-chk001.m4a",
      "text": "いらっしゃいませ～！　旅館『十千万』へようこそ！\n待ってたよ、さくらちゃん！",
      "startTime": 10.8092750312,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chk_01_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_chk_01_01-skr002.m4a",
      "text": "千歌ちゃん\n今日から一泊二日、お世話になります",
      "startTime": 14.4333331983,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tochiman-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tochiman-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chk",
      "speakerName": "高海千歌",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chk.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chk_01_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_chk_01_01-chk002.m4a",
      "text": "ばっちりお世話しちゃうよ！　はぁ～、さくらちゃんが\nまた泊まりに来てくれるなんて夢みたいだよ～！",
      "startTime": 22.7730368378,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tochiman-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tochiman-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chk_01_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_chk_01_01-skr003.m4a",
      "text": "急に来てごめんね。千歌ちゃん達がサニピのライブに\n特別出演することになったでしょ？",
      "startTime": 31.2666651329,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chk_01_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_chk_01_01-skr004.m4a",
      "text": "そのことで、直接会って相談したいことがあったんだ",
      "startTime": 34.3260991815,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tochiman-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tochiman-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chk",
      "speakerName": "高海千歌",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chk.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chk_01_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_chk_01_01-chk003.m4a",
      "text": "さくらちゃんが私に相談？",
      "startTime": 39.1537185434,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tochiman-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tochiman-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chk_01_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_chk_01_01-skr005.m4a",
      "text": "うん。みんなのスケジュールが合わなくて\n代表して私一人で来ることになっちゃって",
      "startTime": 45.9666661502,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tochiman-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tochiman-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chk",
      "speakerName": "高海千歌",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chk.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chk_01_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_chk_01_01-chk004.m4a",
      "text": "でも、最近のサニピは絶好調だよね～。昨日もテレビで\n歌ってるのを観たけど、すっごくキラキラしてたよ！",
      "startTime": 54.4653742556,
      "sfxList": []
    }
